text.section:
Before a registration expires, the registrant may renew it for an additional 2-year term, if the registrant:
otherwise is entitled to be registered;
files with the Commissioner a renewal application on the form that the Commissioner requires;
pays to the Commissioner a renewal fee of $50; and
except as provided in § 8-306(d) of this subtitle, files with the Commissioner evidence of a bond in compliance with § 8-306 of this subtitle.
